## 3. Stability Assessment

### ✅ Strengths

| Area | Implementation | Verdict |
|------|---------------|---------|
| **User Locking** | Redis `SET NX EX` per user | ✅ Solid |
| **Session Management** | Redis-backed with TTL + conversation truncation | ✅ Solid |
| **Retry Logic** | 3 retries with exponential backoff in [OpenClawClient](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/fastapi-wrapper/app/core/moltbot_client.py#24-215) | ✅ Solid |
| **OAuth Flow** | Full init/callback/refresh/revoke with retry | ✅ Solid |
| **Credential Encryption** | Fernet encryption in Supabase | ✅ Solid |
| **Audit Logging** | Every action logged with tokens estimate | ✅ Solid |
| **Multi-tenancy** | `--to agent:main:api:moltbot:dm:user_{userId}` | ✅ Good |
| **Reminder System** | QStash → webhook → SMS delivery | ✅ Good |

### ⚠️ Issues

| Severity | Issue | File |
|----------|-------|------|
| 🔴 **CRITICAL** | `startCommand` uses single Uvicorn worker (not Gunicorn) | [render.yaml L12](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/render.yaml) |
| 🔴 **CRITICAL** | Persistent disk blocks Gateway autoscaling | [render.yaml L107-109](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/render.yaml) |
| 🔴 **CRITICAL** | CLI spawn per request — ~200-400MB RAM each | [server.js L200-250](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/moltbot-gateway/server.js) |
| 🟠 **HIGH** | CORS allows all origins `["*"]` | [main.py](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/fastapi-wrapper/app/main.py) |
| 🟡 **MEDIUM** | No QStash signature verification | [reminders.py L183](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/fastapi-wrapper/app/api/reminders.py) |
| 🟡 **MEDIUM** | 120s timeout ties up workers | [server.js L190](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/moltbot-gateway/server.js) |

**Stability Score: 6/10** — Functional MVP, needs the fixes below.

