| 6 | **Uptime monitoring** (BetterStack/UptimeRobot) | External service | 10 min | Know when it's down |

**Change #1 — In [render.yaml](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/render.yaml):**
```diff
- startCommand: uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT
+ startCommand: gunicorn app.main:app --workers 4 --worker-class uvicorn.workers.UvicornWorker --bind 0.0.0.0:$PORT
```

**Change #2 — In [main.py](file:///e:/Peppi/moltbot-render/fastapi-wrapper/app/main.py):**
```diff
  app.add_middleware(
      CORSMiddleware,
-     allow_origins=settings.ALLOWED_ORIGINS,  # ["*"]
+     allow_origins=["https://peppi.app", "https://peppi-playground.onrender.com"],
```

**After Stage 1**: ~20-30 concurrent users capacity.

